description: Newly renovated three bedroom one bath condominium in highly sought after South Boston. Centrally located and within walking distance to numerous shops, restaurants, both Broadway and Andrew Square redline train stops, Moakley Park and the beach. This unit offers an open floor plan great for entertaining, new stainless steel appliances, custom cabinets, granite counters, hardwood flooring, tiled bath, plenty of natural light, large closets, new central heat & air conditioning systems, laundry and a deck.  Excellent investment opportunity.
